# NAME: Global DNS Providers
# 作用: 确保海外加密 DNS (DoH/DoT/DoQ) 解析请求走代理，防止 DNS 污染与监听
# 更新日期: 2026-07

# >>> Google Public DNS
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,dns.google
DOMAIN,8888.google
IP-CIDR,8.8.8.8/32,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,8.8.4.4/32,no-resolve

# >>> Cloudflare DNS
